data.description: Immaculately kept home with 5 beds, 2.5 baths in the Bedford-Midlands community. From the inviting front porch, you'll step into a dreamy open floor plan with LVP and fresh paint! Formal dining room with coffered ceiling. You'll love the large, gorgeous kitchen with SS appliances, granite countertops, island with storage and power! Laundry room with shelving off the kitchen. Vaulted family room with gas FP. Primary bedroom IS down with trey ceiling, garden tub & separate shower, double sinks. 4 beds upstairs, carpeted with large closets, full bath with double sinks! Step outside - there's a beautiful, privacy fenced yard with plenty of space to relax & enjoy the outdoors - including a spacious patio and hardtop gazebo that stays!! $5K concessions with accepted offer, use it however you choose! Community features clubhouse, pool and gated entrance. Come see it today!
